    "title": "[Bugfix] Disable TRTLLM attention when KV transfer is enabled",
    "user": {
      "login": "ZhanqiuHu",
      "id": 49648934,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ5NjQ4OTM0",
      "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/49648934?v=4",
